Abuja  – The Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) has approved the cancelation of all party primaries in Ebonyi State. The party, which cancelled its governorship, all state House of Assembly and National Assembly primaries in the state, however, charged all aspirants, critical stakeholders, leaders and members of the party in Ebonyi State to remain calm. The party, in a statement by its spokesman, Hon. Debo Ologunagba, said, “After very extensive consultations, deliberations and review of all issues, the National Working Committee (NWC) of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) has approved the cancelation of all party primaries in Ebonyi State. -Advertisement- “To this effect, all state House of Assembly, National Assembly and Governorship primaries of our party in Ebonyi State are hereby cancelled. The NWC will announce new dates for the affected party exercises in the state.” The PDP also charged all aspirants, critical stakeholders, leaders and members of the party in the state to remain united and focused as PDP takes firm steps to rescue the nation from the misrule of the rudderless, corrupt and incompetent All Progressives Congress (APC).